Description: git workflow CLI with guided commits and macros
 Eris is a C-based command-line tool that wraps your everyday git
 workflow in single commands: guided Conventional Commit messages,
 one-shot stage + commit + push, branch creation, rebasing onto the
 base branch, and replayable project macros. A Prolog router lets
 commands chain with and/or/not.
